<loading-screen />

<form class="page-budget-form" bindsubmit="handleSubmit">
  <button-fixed-bottom>
    <view slot="content">
      <view class="input-group">
        <input type="text" placeholder="预算名称" name="name" value="{{ budgetStore.name }}" />
      </view>
      <view class="input-group">
        <input type="number" placeholder="输入金额" name="amount" value="{{ budgetStore.amount }}" />
      </view>
      <view class="input-group">
        <input type="text" placeholder="输入备注" name="remark" value="{{ budgetStore.remark }}" />
      </view>
      <view class="box-tips">
        <view class="title">填写说明：</view>
        <view class="p">按需求分类设置本月预算，如食品每月预算为2000元，日用品每月预算为500元，交通每月预算为500元等；下月重新设置预算，若不设置，则沿用本月的预算；重新设置可以在原有预算的基础上修改或增删</view>
      </view>
    </view>
    <view slot="footer" class="box-footer">
      <button class="btn-primary" form-type="submit">保存</button>
    </view>
  </button-fixed-bottom>
</form>
